{"word":"G2097 - εὐαγγελίζω - euangelízō - yoo-ang-ghel-id'-zo - Declare","slug":"G2097","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐαγγελίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>euangelízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-ang-ghel-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Declare"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03B1;&#x03B3;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x03BB;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - euaggelizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>yoo-ang-ghel-id'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G32\">G32</a>; to <i>announce good</i> news (&ldquo;evangelize&rdquo;) especially the gospel: - declare, bring (declare, show) glad (good) tidings, preach (the gospel)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2098\">G2098</a>, <a href=\"#/G2099\">G2099</a>, <a href=\"#/G4283\">G4283</a>"}]}